## 5. Algorithm Implementation

The core WFC algorithm is implemented as a set of interchangeable strategies for different aspects of the algorithm.

### 5.1 Entropy Calculation Strategies

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   Entropy Calculator                       │
│                                                           │
│  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌───────────┐  │
